title: Google\Cloud\Compute\V1\Network\NetworkFirewallPolicyEnforcementOrder
name: NetworkFirewallPolicyEnforcementOrder
description:
The network firewall policy enforcement order. Can be either AFTER_CLASSIC_FIREWALL or BEFORE_CLASSIC_FIREWALL. Defaults to AFTER_CLASSIC_FIREWALL if the field is not specified.

Protobuf type google.cloud.compute.v1.Network.NetworkFirewallPolicyEnforcementOrder
